        ## Installation
        
        ### Enketo Express
        
        Enketo Express is a full-fledged web application that is often referred to as just "Enketo". It can be used to collect data for any [OpenRosa-compliant server](/openrosa#aggregation). 

        To install an Enketo Express production server for data collection, 
        follow [these instructions](http://blog.enketo.org/install-enketo-production-ubuntu/).

        See the [FAQ](/faq/#troubleshooting-enketo-express) for some common troubleshooting tips for Enketo Express.

        If your organization is already using Heroku, or has particular scaling requirements that Heroku meets well, follow [these instructions](https://github.com/enketo/enketo-express/blob/master/tutorials/02-heroku.md) to deploy Enketo Express on Heroku.
    
